title: EMC Isilon SyncIQ
agents: linux
catalog: os/kernel
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check verifies enabled SyncIQ policies of an EMC Isilon cluster and
 checks each replication for beeing finished within it's schedule. It
 allows some delay, which can be overwritten by WATO rule for each SyncIQ.
 The status of the service is {OK} if last success is within schedule and 
 {WARN} if not. It shows policy name, age of last sucessful sync and
 description.

item:
 Isilon SyncIQ <Policy Name>

inventory:
 One item per Isilon SyncIQ policy is being created.

